N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 262.9 - Sale of processed fish

State Regulations

No person shall sell, offer or expose for sale any
processed fish in New York State unless such processed fish has been processed
and labeled in accordance with the requirements of this Part and any other
applicable statutes or regulations. Notes
